{"metadata":{"title":"countLog","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"let"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"countLog"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"UInt8","preciseIdentifier":"s:s5UInt8V"}],"modules":[{"name":"NordicMesh"}],"symbolKind":"property","externalID":"s:10NordicMesh32ConfigHeartbeatPublicationStatusV8countLogs5UInt8Vvp","roleHeading":"Instance Property","role":"symbol"},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/ConfigHeartbeatPublicationStatus\/countLog","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh","doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/ConfigHeartbeatPublicationStatus"]]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Number of Heartbeat messages remaining to be sent.","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"let","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"countLog","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:s5UInt8V","text":"UInt8","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Possible values:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0x00 - Periodic Heartbeat messages are not published."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0x01 - 0x11 - Number of Heartbeat messages, 2^(n-1), that remain to be sent."}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"0xFF - Periodic Heartbeat messages are published sent indefinitely."}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Other values are prohibited.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The Heartbeat Publication Count Log is a representation of the Heartbeat Publication"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Count state value. The Heartbeat Publication Count Log and Heartbeat Publication Count"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with the value 0x00 and 0x0000 are equivalent. The Heartbeat Publication Count Log"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"value of 0xFF is equivalent to the Heartbeat Publication count value of 0xFFFF."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The Heartbeat Publication Count Log value between 0x01 and 0x11 shall represent that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"smallest integer n where 2^(n-1) is greater than or equal to the Heartbeat Publication"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Count value. For example, if the Heartbeat Publication Count value is 0x0579, then the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Heartbeat Publication Count Log value would be 0x0C."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/configheartbeatpublicationstatus\/countlog"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"references":{"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh":{"abstract":[{"text":"Provision, configure and control Bluetooth mesh devices with nRF Mesh library.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","title":"NordicMesh","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh"},"doc://NordicMesh/documentation/NordicMesh/ConfigHeartbeatPublicationStatus/countLog":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/NordicMesh\/documentation\/NordicMesh\/ConfigHeartbeatPublicationStatus\/countLog","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/nordicmesh\/configheartbeatpublicationstatus\/countlog","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Number of Heartbeat messages remaining to be sent."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"let"},{"kind":"text